OL,3,CSainsbury's plans to axe around 1,500
OL,4,Cjobs in cost-cutting effort
OL,6,FSainsbury's has said it will cut
OL,7,Faround 1,500 roles as part of plans
OL,8,Fthat it hopes will cut costs by around
OL,9,F#1 billion a year.
OL,11,FThe business said that it would cut
OL,12,Froles in its contact centre in Widnes,
OL,13,Fin Cheshire, at its in-store bakeries
OL,14,Fand a few at local fulfilment centres.
OL,16,F"As we move into the next phase of our
OL,17,Fstrategy, we are making some
OL,18,Fdifficult, but necessary decisions,"
OL,19,FChief Executive Simon Roberts said.
