OL,3,CSainsbury's plans to axe around 1,500
OL,4,Cjobs in cost-cutting effort
OL,6,F"I know today's news is unsettling for
OL,7,Faffected colleagues and we will do
OL,8,Feverything we can to support them."
OL,10,FThe supermarket will reduce its
OL,11,Fworkforce by around 1,500 jobs,
OL,12,Fsubject to consultation.
OL,14,FIt said the money it saves will be
OL,15,Freinvested into the business to give
OL,16,Fcustomers "great value, quality and
OL,17,Fservice."
