OL,3,CSainsbury's plans to axe around 1,500
OL,4,Cjobs in cost-cutting effort
OL,6,FAt Widnes a "vast majority" of its
OL,7,Fstaff will see their employment move
OL,8,Fto a different company which
OL,9,FSainsbury's already works with.
OL,11,FAll of Sainsbury's Careline services
OL,12,Fwill now be run by this external
OL,13,Fcompany, Sainsbury's said.
OL,15,FIt also plans to move more of its
OL,16,Fshops "to a more efficient way of
OL,17,Ffreshly baking products".
OL,19,F"As a result, the supermarket will be
OL,20,Fconducting a consultancy process with
OL,21,Fbakers in these stores.
