OL,3,CSainsbury's plans to axe around 1,500
OL,4,Cjobs in cost-cutting effort
OL,6,F"Sainsbury's has reassured affected
OL,7,Fcolleagues that it will find
OL,8,Falternative roles for them where
OL,9,Fpossible, as it will for any colleague
OL,10,Faffected by changes proposed today."
OL,12,FInvestment in technology and
OL,13,Fautomation will also mean that the
OL,14,Fretailer will need fewer local
OL,15,Ffulfilment centres. A "very small
OL,16,Fproportion" of staff will be impacted
OL,17,Fand could be helped to find new roles
OL,18,Fwhere possible.
