OL,3,CSainsbury's plans to axe around 1,500
OL,4,Cjobs in cost-cutting effort
OL,6,FMr Roberts said: "The proposals we've
OL,7,Fbeen talking to teams about today are
OL,8,Fimportant to ensure we're better set
OL,9,Fup to focus on the things that create
OL,10,Fa real impact for our customers,
OL,11,Fdelivering good food for all of us and
OL,12,Fbuilding a platform for growth."
OL,14,FThe company, which is the UK's second-
OL,15,Fbiggest supermarket, said that it
OL,16,Fwould boost the amount of space
OL,17,Fdedicated to food in its 600 stores.
